(\TEDIT.STRIKEOUT.CARET.OFF
  [LAMBDA (TEXTSTREAM TEXTOBJ SEL)                           (* ; "Edited 14-Dec-2023 21:18 by rmk")
                                                            (* ; "Edited 12-Jun-90 18:32 by mitani")
